OL,3,CRoyal Welsh Show 'more relevant than
OL,4,Cever' as it celebrates 120 years
OL,6,FAs the celebrates its 120th birthday,
OL,7,Fthe Royal Welsh Agricultural Society
OL,8,Fsays "It's more relevant than ever".
OL,10,FOn the 26th of February 1904, in
OL,11,FCommittee Room 12 of the Houses of
OL,12,FParliament, what was known as the
OL,13,FWelsh National Agricultural Society
OL,14,Fwas born.
OL,16,FIt was created to raise awareness and
OL,17,Funderstanding of and to promote the
OL,18,Findustry.
