OL,3,CRoyal Welsh Show 'more relevant than
OL,4,Cever' as it celebrates 120 years
OL,6,FAled Jones from the Royal Welsh
OL,7,FAgricultural Society says "Given
OL,8,Frecent events (farmers' protests), I
OL,9,Fthink that's even more relevant now
OL,10,Fthan it was 120 years ago."
OL,12,FFarmers across Wales have staging
OL,13,Fdemonstrations over the new
OL,14,Fsustainable farming scheme - which
OL,15,Fthey fear will lead to 1,000s of job
OL,16,Flosses and damage farm incomes.
OL,18,FThe scheme will replace the grants
OL,19,Fthey used to receive when Britain was
OL,20,Fpart of the European Union.
