OL,3,CRoyal Welsh Show 'more relevant than
OL,4,Cever' as it celebrates 120 years
OL,6,FThe Minister for Rural Affairs Lesley
OL,7,FGriffiths has told WalesOnline that
OL,8,Fshe hopes no farmers will go out of
OL,9,Fbusiness. She says the aim of the
OL,10,Fscheme is "to make sure we secure food
OL,11,Fproduction systems".
OL,13,FShe continued: "It's also about
OL,14,Fsafeguarding the environment and
OL,15,Faddressing the climate and nature
OL,16,Femergency, with both adaptation and
OL,17,Fmitigation."
OL,19,FMs Griffiths added that the Welsh
OL,20,FGovernment "will make changes to the
OL,21,Fscheme" before it is rolled out.
