OL,3,CRoyal Welsh Show 'more relevant than
OL,4,Cever' as it celebrates 120 years
OL,6,FMr Jones says the Royal Welsh Show
OL,7,Fplays a "key role" in giving the
OL,8,Fsector a platform to showcase the
OL,9,Findustry in Wales and has done so
OL,10,Fsince 1904. That year it was held in
OL,11,FAberystwyth and welcomed 5,000
OL,12,Fattendees.
OL,14,FNow staged at , it has grown into the
OL,15,Fbiggest agricultural show in Europe
OL,16,Fattracting people from across the
OL,17,Fworld each year.
