OL,6,FWill Troughton from the National
OL,7,FLibrary of Wales says that by 1908 the
OL,8,Fnumber of attendees had "trebled" from
OL,9,Fthat first show.
OL,11,FHe says in the first year the show ran
OL,12,Fit may have been "elitist" but after
OL,13,Fordinary tenant farmers realised they
OL,14,Ftoo could compete, it "opened the
OL,15,Ffloodgates."
